          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Stakeholders put pressure on executives to redesign software, because redesigning software makes it",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "appear",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "like it’s",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "better",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ". This, matched with the fact that neophiliacs clamor over the slightest of visual design changes means that Apple and Google can continue to sell their products at premium price points even when the actual",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "utility",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "of those products are in sharp decline.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
